        <li>Streamlined Process for Facility Administrators</li>
        <li>Enhanced Security and Compliance</li>
    </ul>
    </div>
    <div >
     <h2>Key Features:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Easy and Intuitive Booking Process</li>
        <li>Secure Handling of Personal Information</li>
        <li>Efficient Slot Management for Correctional Facilities</li>
        <li>User-Friendly Interface for Visitors and Facility Administrators</li>
    </ul>
